Nexus one is o.k, I do have several misgivings (purely as a consumer, not as a dev) some of the misgivings are outlined in this post by Jeff Lemarche.<br><a href="http://iphonedevelopment.blogspot.com/2010/02/nexus-one-from-iphone-developer.html">http://iphonedevelopment.blogspot.com/2010/02/nexus-one-from-iphone-developer.html</a><br>

<br>I would try the droid if the outlined &#39;no-gos&#39; would be a deal breaker for you (as they kinda are for me)<br><br>I am yet to get the droid, but hear its tons better than the Nexus one. <br><br>Best,<br>J. <br>

